17325 { Mips::TLBR, Mips::TLBR, Mips::TLBR_MM },
17326 { Mips::TLBWI, Mips::TLBWI, Mips::TLBWI_MM },
17327 { Mips::TLBWR, Mips::TLBWR, Mips::TLBWR_MM },
17328 { Mips::TLT, Mips::TLT, Mips::TLT_MM },
17329 { Mips::TLTI, Mips::TLTI, Mips::TLTI_MM },
17330 { Mips::TLTU, Mips::TLTU, Mips::TLTU_MM },
17331 { Mips::TNE, Mips::TNE, Mips::TNE_MM },
17332 { Mips::TNEI, Mips::TNEI, Mips::TNEI_MM },
17333 { Mips::TRUNC_W_D32, Mips::TRUNC_W_D32, Mips::TRUNC_W_MM },
17334 { Mips::TRUNC_W_S, Mips::TRUNC_W_S, Mips::TRUNC_W_S_MM },
17335 { Mips::TTLTIU, Mips::TTLTIU, Mips::TLTIU_MM },
17336 { Mips::UDIV, Mips::UDIV, Mips::UDIV_MM },
17337 { Mips::WAIT, Mips::WAIT, Mips::WAIT_MM },
17338 { Mips::WSBH, Mips::WSBH, Mips::WSBH_MM },
17339 { Mips::XOR, Mips::XOR, Mips::XOR_MM },
17340 { Mips::XORi, Mips::XORi, Mips::XORi_MM },
17341}; // End of Std2MicroMipsTable
17342
17343 unsigned mid;
17344 unsigned start = 0;
17345 unsigned end = 266;
17346 while (start < end) {
17347 mid = start + (end - start) / 2;
17348 if (Opcode == Std2MicroMipsTable[mid][0]) {
17349 break;
17350 }
17351 if (Opcode < Std2MicroMipsTable[mid][0])
17352 end = mid;
17353 else
17354 start = mid + 1;
17355 }
17356 if (start == end)
17357 return -1; // Instruction doesn't exist in this table.
17358
17359 if (inArch == Arch_se)
17360 return Std2MicroMipsTable[mid][1];
17361 if (inArch == Arch_micromips)
17362 return Std2MicroMipsTable[mid][2];
17363 return -1;}
17364
17365// Std2MicroMipsR6
17366LLVM_READONLY
17367int Std2MicroMipsR6(uint16_t Opcode, enum Arch inArch) {
17368static const uint16_t Std2MicroMipsR6Table[][3] = {
17369 { Mips::ADD, Mips::ADD, Mips::ADD_MMR6 },
17370 { Mips::ADDiu, Mips::ADDiu, Mips::ADDIU_MMR6 },
17371 { Mips::ADDu, Mips::ADDu, Mips::ADDU_MMR6 },
17372 { Mips::AND, Mips::AND, Mips::AND_MMR6 },
